park avenue provides the stylish man-about-town with all the essentials he needs to look his best. Wear these park avenue sunglasses to look stylish while out and about in the sunshine.
The glasses come in a leather-look case with branding on the front and a zip fastening, cloth included to clean the lenses.

Lens width: 60 mm
Lens colour: Graduated brown
Frame colour: Brown tones

UV protection
Stylish shaped metal frame
Acrylic arm socks provide a comfortable Fit
Flexible hinges for fit
Rubber pads to hold the glasses in place, ensuring there is no friction with the skin

Care
Polish with cloth to remove dust
Do not put your sunglasses face down on a table or on heated areas like the dashboard of a car
Keep in the original case in a dry place at a temperature between -10° C and +35° C
